{"tid":2425974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"市民於紅石門坳報警後由公安接線","createTime":"2021-02-27T16:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T20:16:30.000Z","uid":227929,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"edb2b0fdb320340e3fb3cf06fc250036a3e76299","tid":2425974,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:50:29.000Z","msg":"2月26日下午，一名24歲男子獨自由烏蛟騰起行，打算行至紅石門。該男子疑迷路嘗試報警求助，但身處地點未有本地網絡覆蓋。直至午夜，電話訊號成功接通內地緊急求助專綫，隨即由內地通報。警方、消防、民安隊及飛行服務隊人員分別登山和在空中搜救。 直至今日(2月27日) 下午，於紅石門坳尋獲該名男子，他清醒毋須送院，由家人陪伴離開。<br />\n<br />\n警方提醒市民，切勿忽視行山的危險性，出發前應根據個人能力規劃行程，量力而為。留意當日天氣預報，切勿單獨出發，應預先把行程告知家人或朋友。迷路時，應循原路折返。如有需要，應盡快尋求協助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hyicy5V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHyicy5V.jpg&h=9b415c5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pXB9Bjg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpXB9Bjg.jpg&h=ea0bca72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來已經同大陸接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9b3d749bceca031625c528e247669b2c27daaf","tid":2425974,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"btw幸苦曬各位民安隊員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e646861145087174079c153acbae67cfe7a153","tid":2425974,"uid":332457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:51:46.000Z","msg":"條友驚到瀨尿？"},{"pid":"132bd92dd06a4b3b71e62e083404a6633f533c00","tid":2425974,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60e646861145087174079c153acbae67cfe7a153","tid":2425974,"uid":332457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:51:46.000Z","msg":"條友驚到瀨尿？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:57:52.000Z","msg":"點解咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe188deade106b0cfac906c0193b534d155a4e2d","tid":2425974,"uid":165232,"like":0,"dislike":9,